description: BMO International Dividend ETF has been designed to provide exposure to a yield weighted portfolio of dividend equities domiciled in international developed markets (outside North America). The ETF utilizes a rules based methodology that considers three-year dividend growth rate, yield, and payout ratio to invest in international equities. Securities will also be subject to a liquidity screen process. The underlying portfolio is rebalanced in May and reconstituted in November.
name: BMO International Dividend ETF
